EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO HEALTH AND SAFETY -- PUBLIC HEALTH AND WORKPLACE SAFETY
ACT
***
1 This act would provide that any law or regulation which prohibits or protects a person from
2 exposure to second hand smoke would be deemed to also be a prohibition or protection from
3 exposure to second-hand marijuana smoke or vapor, regardless of how the smoke or vapor was
4 generated.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
